The paper also presents simulation results, which involve multimedia systems and applications, suggesting cs.MM (Multimedia) as a possible category. The paper also deals with the behavior of the IEEE 802.11 protocol, which is a topic related to system dynamics and control, suggesting cs.SY (Systems and Control) as another possible category. Finally, the paper proposes a fairness criterion, which is a topic related to game theory and mechanism design, suggesting cs.PF (Performance) as a possible category.
